# Setting an Initial Password for Windows Instance from a OCI Vault Secret


The manual provides PS scripts to retrieve a secret from OCI Vault and update the Windows password for the OPC account.
[OCI Cloud-Init WinPwd Update](https://github.com/Olygo/CloudInit_WinPwd_Update#oci-cloud-init-winpwd-update)

